# restic exclude patterns — copy to ops/backup/exclude.txt (gitignored) and
# point RESTIC_EXCLUDE_FILE at it. One pattern per line; restic matches these
# against full paths. These drop regenerable bulk so snapshots stay lean.

# Dependency + build caches (reinstallable)
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/venv
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/target
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/.turbo

# Package/manager + app caches
**/.cache
**/Library/Caches
**/Caches
**/.gradle
**/.cargo/registry

# OS cruft
**/.DS_Store
**/.Trash
**/*.swp

# Large regenerable derived data (kept in git / re-derivable)
**/derived
